### Key decisions
- `[SYSTEM_PROMPT]` absence check prevents collision with Ministral 3 (which also uses `[INST]`/`[/INST]`)
- `<s>` BOS only on first turn; subsequent turns start bare `[INST]`
- `COMMON_CHAT_FORMAT_CONTENT_ONLY` — no PEG parser, grammar, or preserved_tokens needed
- `common/chat.h` is **not modified**
